407
00:21:27,740 --> 00:21:30,460
Su Shunqin, Wang Yaochen,
you two are the main writers.

408
00:21:31,500 --> 00:21:32,580
Wen Yanbo, you proofread it.

409
00:21:33,460 --> 00:21:34,700
Before today’s sunset,

410
00:21:35,860 --> 00:21:37,820
