411
00:21:42,860 --> 00:21:45,020
- Your Majesty. - Your Majesty.

412
00:21:45,780 --> 00:21:47,900
- Your Majesty. - Your Majesty.

413
00:21:48,580 --> 00:21:50,500
You are different

414
00:21:50,500 --> 00:21:51,540
from the former emperors.

415
00:22:03,060 --> 00:22:03,660
Your Majesty.

416
00:22:03,660 --> 00:22:04,460
Sir.

417
00:22:12,020 --> 00:22:14,980
When the former emperors

418
00:22:14,980 --> 00:22:15,980
led the troop,

419
00:22:16,420 --> 00:22:17,660
