446
00:24:03,140 --> 00:24:04,420
Thank you, sir.

447
00:24:04,980 --> 00:24:06,260
You enlightened me.

448
00:24:14,660 --> 00:24:15,500
Today

449
00:24:17,580 --> 00:24:19,100
