458
00:24:46,300 --> 00:24:47,050
Your Majesty.

459
00:24:47,060 --> 00:24:48,220
Your Majesty.

460
00:24:51,500 --> 00:24:53,220
His Majesty

461
00:24:53,220 --> 00:24:54,900
doesn’t want to see any officials

462
00:24:55,540 --> 00:24:57,580
