487
00:26:20,910 --> 00:26:21,910
Nothing is inappropriate.

488
00:26:23,390 --> 00:26:24,110
It’s just the sentence

489
00:26:25,030 --> 00:26:26,590
“I am concerned about the world.

490
00:26:26,870 --> 00:26:28,270
I can be of a high ranking,

491
00:26:28,790 --> 00:26:30,030
