493
00:26:32,390 --> 00:26:34,030
I can be a teacher in a small village,

494
00:26:34,190 --> 00:26:35,630
and I shall still do the same”

495
00:26:35,990 --> 00:26:37,270
is different from the rest.

496
00:26:53,030 --> 00:26:53,870
His Majesty held my hand

497
00:26:55,590 --> 00:26:57,510
to write that sentence.

498
00:26:59,430 --> 00:27:03,030
When Fan Zhongyan was fighting against Lv Yijian,

499
00:27:04,270 --> 00:27:05,630
I didn’t know what His Majesty’s attitude was,

500
00:27:07,230 --> 00:27:08,390
so he wrote this

501
00:27:09,110 --> 00:27:10,430
