516
00:27:51,500 --> 00:27:54,220
Our eloquence is nowhere near
as good as His Majesty.

517
00:27:54,540 --> 00:27:56,140
That feels terrible.

518
00:27:56,860 --> 00:27:57,940
I didn’t expect that

519
00:27:58,220 --> 00:28:01,260
courtly and reserved as Deputy Censor Yan is,

520
00:28:01,420 --> 00:28:04,140
