537
00:28:39,980 --> 00:28:42,340
That’s why he could give a name so quickly.

538
00:28:42,900 --> 00:28:45,980
His Majesty is kind and benevolent,

539
00:28:46,380 --> 00:28:48,620
but others’ words

540
00:28:48,620 --> 00:28:49,820
