542
00:28:52,980 --> 00:28:55,460
I learned so much today.

543
00:29:02,260 --> 00:29:03,020
Before

544
00:29:04,260 --> 00:29:05,780
I criticized you in my heart

545
00:29:07,980 --> 00:29:11,540
