559
00:29:48,980 --> 00:29:49,940
Zimei is highly talented

560
00:29:50,860 --> 00:29:52,540
and devoted to state affairs.

561
00:29:53,220 --> 00:29:54,540
You are the ideal scholar

562
00:29:55,180 --> 00:29:57,100
