567
00:30:40,460 --> 00:30:41,380
But it doesn’t matter.

568
00:30:42,980 --> 00:30:44,020
Thank you for accompanying me.

569
00:30:47,340 --> 00:30:48,540
And thank you

570
00:30:49,620 --> 00:30:50,540
